</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="38" pageNumber="39" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1437,798,2013]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,1266,1292]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
This is the only species with ocelli strongly elevated above vertex, median mesoscutal line present at least at the most posterior end, and antenna with 14 flagellomeres. Also see the key.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
